    <h1>INTRODUCTION</h1>
    <hr />
    <p>
        2025 1st FPT International Conference on Emerging Trends in Computing - FECTC 2025 is organised by FPT University, Vietnam, Cantho Campus, on August 30th - 31st, 2025.
    </p>
    <p>
        The FCETC 2025 offers a range of engaging activities for both local and international experts, including pre-conference workshops, team-building sessions, and entertainment activities, followed by keynote presentations and in-depth discussion panels. These panels will focus on cutting-edge AI technologies and their applications in real-world scenarios.
    </p>
    <p>
        In particular, FCETC 2025 aims to:
        <ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
            <li>Showcase the latest breakthroughs in AI research and their practical applications in sectors such as healthcare, finance, manufacturing, and transportation.</li>
            <li>Promote professional dialogue on emerging trends and challenges in AI development, deployment, and ethics.</li>
            <li>Provide constructive feedback on potential research papers to foster the future growth of AI studies.</li>
            <li>Encourage collaboration between universities, independent researchers, and companies to translate research findings into practical applications.</li>
            <li>Strengthen partnerships between FPT University and domestic and international institutions, contributing to global progress in AI research and development.</li>
        </ul>

    </p>
