    <hr />
    <p>
        This conference covers, but is not limited to, the following key AI-related topics:
        <ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
            <li>Machine Learning</li>
            <li>Deep Learning</li>
            <li>Natural Language Processing (NLP)</li>
            <li>Computer Vision</li>
            <li>Robotics and Automation</li>
            <li>Explainable AI (XAI)</li>
            <li>Interactive AI</li>
            <li>AI in Healthcare</li>
            <li>Distributed AI</li>
            <li>AI and the Internet of Things (IoT)</li>
            <li>AI in Finance</li>
            <li>AI in Education</li>
            <li>AI in Transportation</li>
            <li>AI in Arts and Entertainment</li>
            <li>AI and Data Science</li>
            <li>Multimodal AI</li>
            <li>AI in Cybersecurity</li>
            <li>AI in Energy</li>
            <li>AI in Mental Health</li>

        </ul>
    </p>
